2ï¸âƒ£ Convert Accuracy â†’ Heatmap Intensity

Create color buckets (simple + interpretable).

Accuracy	Color Meaning
0â€“30%	ğŸ”´ Weak
31â€“60%	ğŸŸ  Needs Practice
61â€“80%	ğŸŸ¡ Good
81â€“100%	ğŸŸ¢ Mastered

Backend helper:

def mastery_level(acc):
    if acc <= 30: return "weak"
    if acc <= 60: return "practice"
    if acc <= 80: return "good"
    return "mastered"
